105
00:10:41,025 --> 00:10:41,984
No…

106
00:10:43,486 --> 00:10:44,737
That's not true…

107
00:10:49,367 --> 00:10:51,953
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

108
00:10:56,124 --> 00:10:58,126
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

109
00:10:58,209 --> 00:10:59,127
Eun Yeong-ro!

110
00:11:00,294 --> 00:11:01,129
Eun Yeong-ro!

111
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,508
-Yeong-ro!
-Yeong-u!

112
00:11:07,385 --> 00:11:10,388
Let go! Let go of me!

113
00:11:10,972 --> 00:11:12,056
Calm down!

114
00:11:13,850 --> 00:11:15,768
I need to go see for myself!

115
00:11:19,355 --> 00:11:21,482
It's dangerous.
You don't want to die, do you?

116
00:11:49,677 --> 00:11:51,637
You're the leader of those
who killed Yeong-u?

117
00:11:52,805 --> 00:11:54,557
You evil bastard.

118
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:57,435
Holding us hostage wasn't enough?
Why did you kill my brother?

119
00:11:57,518 --> 00:11:59,187
What did he do wrong?

120
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:01,481
He didn't do anything to deserve it!

121
00:12:04,066 --> 00:12:05,401
Bring him back.

122
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:07,904
Bring him back!

