fighting against spies from the North.

239
00:24:02,117 --> 00:24:04,328
If only it weren't for Operation Phoenix…

240
00:24:06,455 --> 00:24:07,623
If Code 1 finds out

241
00:24:07,706 --> 00:24:10,334
you blame the operation for it,
you'll be doomed!

242
00:24:10,792 --> 00:24:12,920
Now that the operation has failed,

243
00:24:13,504 --> 00:24:15,005
if you're pushed out,

244
00:24:15,088 --> 00:24:16,215
what about Yeong-ro?

245
00:24:16,298 --> 00:24:18,425
We can't bring Yeong-u back,

246
00:24:18,509 --> 00:24:20,719
but we must save Yeong-ro at all cost!

247
00:24:21,220 --> 00:24:23,347
I know you made a deal with the North,

248
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:27,851
