those brutal spies, she can never be safe.

249
00:24:28,435 --> 00:24:30,229
Honey!

250
00:24:31,230 --> 00:24:33,774
You must pull yourself together!

251
00:24:34,441 --> 00:24:36,985
I know. I know that.

252
00:24:37,778 --> 00:24:38,987
Yeong-u…

253
00:24:39,363 --> 00:24:40,864
Yeong-u…

254
00:24:44,952 --> 00:24:46,703
<i>And I'll look out for her</i>

255
00:24:47,204 --> 00:24:49,623
